                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18780806-702-offence-1 t18780806-name-208"></join>Joseph Mendelstam</persName>, his master. <hi rend="italic">Second Count</hi> charging both prisoners with feloniously receiving the same.</rs>
